@section Getting Ready

In order  to play in Tootsville,  you'll need a computer  of some kind
with certain minimum capabilities.

You   can    find   these    requirements   in   the    Wiki-Wiki   at
@url{https://wiki.tootsville.org/wiki/System_Requirements}

You   can   also  test   your   system's   capabilities  by   visiting
@url{https://play.tootsville.org/play/system-check/}

For best results, we recommend playing using the latest version of the
Mozilla Firefox@registered{} web browser. If  you have a different web
browser, like Chrome or Edge, you can probably still play the game, or
you can upgrade to Firefox by visiting @url{https://getfirefox.com/}

There is also a  link on the main menu (the  menu accessed by clicking
on the circled  T logo at the  top-left corner of the  game screen) to
download   Firefox    if   you   begin   playing    the   game   using
a different browser.

@node Signing In
@section Signing In

You'll sign in to Tootsville using your Google account.

If you're already logged in to Google when you visit the site, you'll just
be asked to authorize Tootsville once.

If you aren't yet signed in to your Google account, you'll have the
opportunity to do so.

Once  you've signed  in, you'll  go  directly to  your Toot  character
selection screen.

