@section Troops and Operators

Tootsville players may  volunteer to join the ranks of  the Toot Troops.
This  is  an  organization  who  help new  players  and  keep  the  game
running smoothly.

WRITEME

Some players are  invited to be Tootsville Operators.  Operators can see
``behind the curtains'' into the inner workings of Tootsville.

WRITEME

Some operators are  Builder Toots. Builder Toots  actually construct the
game itself, including arranging public spaces like Toot Square.

